ðŸ“š Book Management API

A RESTful API for managing books and users. Users can create books, view all books with filters, and checkout books. Built with Node.js, Express, MongoDB, and TypeScript.

Features

User Management

Register and login users (JWT authentication)

Track borrowed books

Book Management

Create books (author automatically assigned from logged-in user)

Get all books with filters (genre, available stock, published year)

Checkout books (updates stock and user borrowed list)

Author info populated in responses

Validations

Required fields validation

Stock must be positive integer

Prevent duplicate book titles (case-insensitive)

Tech Stack

Node.js

Express.js

MongoDB & Mongoose

TypeScript

JWT for authentication